"Baalɛɛnɩ" kɛ kpakpayaɣ sɔsɔɔ nakɛyɛ.

Tɔmpiye "Baalɛɛnɩ" lɩna [[Latɛŋ kʊnʊŋ|Laatɛɛ]] kʋnʋŋ taa. Kʋnʋŋ ŋgʋ kɩ-taa lɛ, payaɣ se ''ballaena'' yaa ''ballena'' yaa ɖɔɖɔ se ''balaena''. [[Latɛŋ kʊnʊŋ|Laatɛɛ]] tɔmpiye ɖɩnɛ, ɖɩnɩɣzɩna [[Krɛsɩ kɩbɩnʊʊ kʊnʊŋ|Krɛɛkɩ]] tɔmpiye ''phalaina'' pʋ-tɔbʋʋ se mbʋ puhuu yɔ. [[Krɛsɩ kɩbɩnʊʊ kʊnʊŋ|Krɛɛkɩ]] nɛ Rooma n̄ɩma pɔ-cɔzɔnaa tɔma se baalɛɛnɩ kɛ lɩm tɛɛ kɩpnɛ nɖɩ ɖɩwɛna hʋzɩŋ yɔ. 

[[File:Adult Humpback Whale breaching.jpg|thumb|Balɛɛnɩ kikulumuu ([[Fransɩɩ kʊnʊŋ|fransɩɩ]] : ''Baleine à bosse''; [[Englɩsɩɩ kʊnʊŋ|Eŋglɩsɩɩ]]: ''Humpback Whale''). Cɩnɛ ɖɩnaɣ se kɩlɩɩ lɩm taa nɛ kɩma.]]

Ŋgʋ lɩm tɛɛ kpakpasɩ lɛɛsɩ fɛyɩna hʋzɩŋ. [[Franɩɩ (France)|Fransɩɩ]] n̄ɔtɔŋ se, pɩkɛ lɩm tɛɛ kpakpayaɣ n̄azɩ n̄azʋʋ ŋga pɔyɔɔdɩ kɔ-tɔm Ɛsɔtɔm takayaɣ taa se kiliba Yoonaasɩ nɛ ɛlɛ caɣ ko-lotu taa kɩyakɩŋ naatozo yɔ. Paya n̄azɩ n̄azʋʋ ŋgʋ se kpakpayaɣ, ɛlɛ, toovenum lɛ, paakpakɩɣ-kʋ se kɩkɛ kpakpayaɣ siŋŋ.

